                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-dpm                 .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non trovato : a materia prima *
      *                      * successiva                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to stp-srt-inp-200.
       stp-srt-inp-250.
